# Gotchas Archive

This archive holds historical or niche gotchas that are not needed for default onboarding.
Use this file when investigating regressions in legacy workflows, old run artifacts, or
rare operational edge cases.

## Scope

- Historical "(fixed)" failure patterns
- Rare environment-specific issues
- Deep pipeline edge-case notes not required for day-to-day implementation

## Source of Truth

- Live, high-signal gotchas remain in `gotchas-agent.mdc`.
- Canonical behavior still comes from `src/` and `.cursor/docs/*`.
